---
source: crates/runtime/tests/models/search.rs
description: "SELECT id, answer FROM vector_search(qs_view, 'second', answer) order by _score desc, id LIMIT 4"
---
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                            |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer).id, vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer).answer                                                            |
|               |   Sort: vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer)._score DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer).id ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=4                       |
|               |     Projection: vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer).id, vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer).answer, vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer)._score |
|               |       TableScan: vector_search(qs_view, Utf8("second"), answer) projection=[_score, answer, id]                                                                                 |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[id@0 as id, answer@1 as answer]                                                                                                                           |
|               |   SortPreservingMergeExec: [_score@2 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], fetch=4                                                                                                        |
|               |     SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[_score@2 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                            |
|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[CAST(key@1 AS Int64) as id, answer@0 as answer, 1 - distance@2 as _score]                                                                           |
|               |         CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                  |
|               |             BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |               CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                 S3VectorsQueryExec (INDEX_NAME_1): limit=100                                                                                                                    |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                 |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
